rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0001
rows.name:
The Grail Metsu looks to be as
formidable an opponent as they say.

rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0002
rows.name:
Your Majesty, you do not
have to do this.

rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0004
rows.name:
Letting the Iiran seal fall into Metsu's
hands would be unthinkable.

rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0005
rows.name: The thought of it makes me shudder.

rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0006
rows.name:
Yes. We have to put him down
once and for all.

rows.label: campfev11_560_100_msg0009
rows.name: Let's give it everything we've got.
